textAnnotations.description:
S0,THE EVIL PRESIDENT
VETOED THE EXPANDED
SCHIP PROGRAM FORCING
POOR TIMMY'S PARENTS
TO PROVIDE HIS HEALTH
CARE ON A MEAGER
$80,000 A YEAR INCOM..
AS A RESULT, POOR
TIMMY DIDN'T GET
A PLAYSTATION3 AND
HIS DAD DIDN'T GET
THAT NEW BMW-AND
NO ONE LIVED HAPPILY
EVER AFTER.
BUSH
8g
ㄩ
